# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# Shared Credentials — Workspace Level (all brands)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to credentials_shared.env and fill values.
# credentials_shared.env is gitignored — never commit real tokens.
#
# These are workspace-wide tools (not brand-specific).
# Brand-specific tokens → brands/{slug}/credentials.env

# ── Slack ──
# SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=xoxb-...

# ── ClickUp ──
# CLICKUP_API_TOKEN=pk_...

# ── Google Suite (Drive, Calendar, Gmail, Sheets) ──
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
# GOOGLE_REFRESH_TOKEN=

# ── Other workspace tools ──
# Add as needed. One line per variable.
